  <bioghist id="aspace_84927783432d5494ce50d4a0528650a5">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Plant physiologist; professor of botany, Cornell University.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_12025210c7faf1b852c26bceb3cf506e">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Articles and notes concerning plants as a source of rubber, including guayule and kok-saghyz; papers pertaining to the Ninth Annual Chemurgie Conference. Also, photocopy of bound manuscript containing "A Brief History of the Department of Botany" by Lewis Knudson, October 15, 1938, and menu and guest list from Botany Department dinner, 1938.</p>  </scopecontent>
